channel.desc: Horror, Sci-Fi, Mystery 2019 A sketchy real estate agent leads Tom and Gemma to a neighborhood of identical houses to buy a new home. As they try to escape the maze, they find only one way out. This film received an award at Cannes Film Festival 2019. Imogen Poots, Jesse Eisenberg, Danielle Ryan, Jonathan Aris, Molly McCann, Lorcan Finnegan, Lorcan Finnegan, Garret Shanley.
